{"title":"ABAP TLDR","uid":"129a08e03d29887e85b5514f858d5c9d","slug":"abap-00-tldr","date":"2022-11-06T17:26:56.164Z","updated":"2022-11-06T17:31:56.591Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/abap-00-tldr.json","keywords":["SAP","ABAP","Learn","Aprender","Software","Programação","Desenvolvimento","Desenvolvimento de Software"],"cover":"/img/default-cover.png","content":"<p>ABAP TLDR <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/TL;DR\">(Too long; didn’t Read)</a> é uma tentativa de conteúdo prático e objetivo sobre a linguagem de programação ABAP e que possa servir de referência durante os primeiros passos da jornada de um desenvolvedor SAP.</p>\n<p>O conteúdo é destinado a quem deseja uma rápida visão geral sobre a linguagem de programação ABAP.</p>\n<BR/>\n\n<h3 id=\"ABAP\"><a href=\"#ABAP\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"ABAP\"></a>ABAP</h3><p>ABAP é uma linguagem de programação proprietária criada pela <a href=\"https://g.co/kgs/BqU1oG\">SAP SE</a>. </p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>Principais Caracteristicas:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Linguagem de alto nível, tipada &amp; orientada a objetos</li>\n<li>Acesso integrado a tabelas de qualquer banco de dados (OpenSQL)</li>\n<li>Retrocompatibilidade entre todas as suas versões.</li>\n</ul></blockquote>\n<BR/>\n\n<h3 id=\"Sintaxe\"><a href=\"#Sintaxe\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Sintaxe\"></a>Sintaxe</h3><p><code>&lt;ABAP KEYWORD&gt;</code> <code>&lt;IDENTIFIERS | OPERATORS| EXPRESSIONS &gt;</code> <code>&lt;END STATEMENT&gt;</code><br><code>Basic Syntax</code></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-abap\" data-language=\"abap\"><code class=\"language-abap\"><span class=\"token keyword\">CONSTANTS</span> hello <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> char5 <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Olá'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">CONSTANTS</span> world <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> char5 <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Mundo!'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">CONSTANTS</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">space</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> char1 <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token string\">' '</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">WRITE</span> hello <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">space</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> world<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><code>Chained Statements</code></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-abap\" data-language=\"abap\"><code class=\"language-abap\"><span class=\"token keyword\">REPLACE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'A'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">WITH</span> <span class=\"token string\">'B'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">INTO</span> firstname<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">REPLACE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'A'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">WITH</span> <span class=\"token string\">'B'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">INTO</span> lastname<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-abap\" data-language=\"abap\"><code class=\"language-abap\"><span class=\"token keyword\">REPLACE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'A'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">WITH</span> <span class=\"token string\">'B'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">INTO</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> firstname<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> lastname<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><code>Comments (*) | (&quot;)</code></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-abap\" data-language=\"abap\"><code class=\"language-abap\"><span class=\"token comment\">* ------------------------------------------------ *</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">*  Programa: RESERVAS</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">*  Autor: ABAP Developer</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">* ------------------------------------------------ *</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">REPORT</span> BOOKINGS<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">* Recupera os dados das reservas de hospedagem do banco de dados</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">SELECT</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">FROM</span> booking_info\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">WHERE</span> accommodation_type <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'S'</span>          <span class=\"token eol-comment comment\">\" Reservas em Suites</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">AND</span> check_in_date     <span class=\"token operator\">>=</span> sy_datum<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>    <span class=\"token eol-comment comment\">\" A partir da data atual</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"Tipos-de-Dados-Locais\"><a href=\"#Tipos-de-Dados-Locais\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Tipos de Dados Locais\"></a>Tipos de Dados Locais</h3><p><code>Numeric Types</code></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-abap\" data-language=\"abap\"><code class=\"language-abap\"><span class=\"token keyword\">DATA</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> \n    v_int        <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">i</span>          <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token number\">2147483647</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>       \n    v_int8       <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> int8       <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token number\">9223372036854775807</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    v_decfloat16 <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> decfloat16 <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token number\">4611686018427387904</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    v_decfloat34 <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> decfloat34 <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>8948022309329048855892746252172e+<span class=\"token number\">76</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>Outros tipos numéricos: <a href=\"https://help.sap.com/doc/abapdocu_751_index_htm/7.51/en-us/abenbuiltin_types_numeric.htm\">B (1-Byte), S (2-Byte), F (Float 8-Byte), P (Packed 1-16 Bytes)</a></p>\n<p><code>Character-Like Types</code></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-abap\" data-language=\"abap\"><code class=\"language-abap\"><span class=\"token keyword\">DATA</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> \n    v_char           <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">c</span>       <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'ABC123'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">LENGTH</span> <span class=\"token number\">6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    v_number_char<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> n       <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'123456'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    v_string         <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> string  <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Hello World!'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><code>DateTime Types</code></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-abap\" data-language=\"abap\"><code class=\"language-abap\"><span class=\"token keyword\">DATA</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> \n    v_data <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> d <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token number\">20221022</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>    <span class=\"token eol-comment comment\">\" YYYYMMDD -> User Format -> 22-10-2022</span>\n    v_hora <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> t <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token number\">213200</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>      <span class=\"token eol-comment comment\">\" HHMMSS   -> User Format -> 21:32:00</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><code>Byte-Like Types</code></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-abap\" data-language=\"abap\"><code class=\"language-abap\"><span class=\"token keyword\">DATA</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> \n    v_xstring <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> xstring <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'20C4DD6DD965AF'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    v_hex<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  <span class=\"token keyword\">TYPE</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">x</span>       <span class=\"token keyword\">VALUE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'FF'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n","text":"ABAP TLDR (Too long; didn’t Read) é uma tentativa de conteúdo prático e objetivo sobre a linguagem de programação ABAP e que possa servir de...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.3k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Guias","slug":"Guias","count":2,"path":"api/categories/Guias.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Guia ABAP","slug":"Guia-ABAP","count":8,"path":"api/tags/Guia-ABAP.json"},{"name":"Overview","slug":"Overview","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Overview.json"},{"name":"Cheatsheet","slug":"Cheatsheet","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Cheatsheet.json"},{"name":"Micro Learning","slug":"Micro-Learning","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Micro-Learning.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#ABAP\"><span class=\"toc-text\">ABAP</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Sintaxe\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Sintaxe</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Tipos-de-Dados-Locais\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Tipos de Dados Locais</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"ABAP Academy","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/img/abap-academy-logo-bg.png","link":"/","description":"Guias e conteúdos práticos sobre programação ABAP de forma gratuíta, simples e descomplicada. Autor: Edmilson de Assis Abreu","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/abap-academy/abap-academy.github.io","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"ABAP: Tipos de Dados","uid":"46768f5dde918bb1b3c6a0857f888585","slug":"abap-04-data","date":"2022-11-06T17:26:56.925Z","updated":"2022-11-07T21:04:51.421Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/abap-04-data.json","keywords":["SAP","ABAP","Learn","Aprender","Software","Programação","Desenvolvimento","Desenvolvimento de Software"],"cover":"/img/default-cover.png","text":"Todas as linguagens de pro